OL,3,CConservation 'milestone' at sanctuary
OL,4,Cfor smaller wildcats
OL,6,FA Eurasian lynx rescued from Ukraine
OL,7,Fhas taken her first steps on grass and
OL,8,Fin her UK forever home as new
OL,9,F"milestone" habitats at a sanctuary in
OL,10,FKent were officially opened.
OL,12,FUrsa had been living in a 44
OL,13,Fconverted horse stables for the last
OL,14,Fthree years in the war zone before
OL,15,Fbeing brought to Kent by the Big Cat
OL,16,FSanctuary in February.
OL,18,FThe young wildcat has since been
OL,19,Fliving in an outdoor habitat there
OL,20,Funtil the new enclosure was ready to
OL,21,Fmove into.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@KO]tD@\OZ
