OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784900897
OL,3,CConservation 'milestone' at sanctuary
OL,4,Cfor smaller wildcats
OL,6,FThe Small Cat Rescue Centre is a state-
OL,7,Fof-the-art facility complete with
OL,8,Fwalkways and climbing systems.
OL,10,FUrsa will live there alongside three
OL,11,Fsmall wildcats, fellow Eurasian lynx,
OL,12,FRhys, Blob, a bobcat and Boson, a
OL,13,Ffishing cat, who were rescued from the
OL,14,FCat Survival Trust in Hertfordshire in
OL,15,FJanuary 2025.
OL,17,FElsewhere the sanctuary also opened
OL,18,Fthe Rusty-Spotted Cat Conservation
OL,19,FCentre, the UK's largest habitat for
OL,20,Fthe world's smallest wildcat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
