FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784900897
OL,3,CConservation 'milestone' at sanctuary
OL,4,Cfor smaller wildcats
OL,6,FRusty-spotted cats weigh as little as
OL,7,F0.9kg and are comparable in size to a
OL,8,Fred squirrel.
OL,10,FThe facility aims to mimic the cats'
OL,11,Fnative environments in India, Sri
OL,12,FLanka and Nepal.
OL,14,FThe Big Cat Sanctuary's managing
OL,15,Fdirector and conservationist, Cam
OL,16,FWhitnall, said: "Today represents a
OL,17,Fhuge milestone not only for our
OL,18,Fsanctuary, but for the future
OL,19,Fconservation of smaller wildcat
OL,20,Fspecies globally.
OL,26,@xD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
