OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784900897
OL,3,CConservation 'milestone' at sanctuary
OL,4,Cfor smaller wildcats
OL,6,F"While the larger apex predators often
OL,7,Fdominate the headlines, these smaller
OL,8,Fcats face severe threats in the wild
OL,9,Ffrom habitat loss and human
OL,10,Fencroachment.
OL,12,F"By combining world-class welfare with
OL,13,Fcutting-edge technology, we are
OL,14,Fsecuring a sustainable future
OL,15,Fpopulation and ensuring these
OL,16,Fremarkable animals are no longer
OL,17,Foverlooked.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784900897
OL,3,CConservation 'milestone' at sanctuary
OL,4,Cfor smaller wildcats
OL,6,F"Rusty-spotted cats are classified as
OL,7,F"near threatened" and the enclosure
OL,8,Fuses technology such as climate
OL,9,Fcontrol, specialist UV lighting and
OL,10,Frainfall systems to replicate natural
OL,11,Fweather patterns."
OL,13,FSo far the centre is home to male
OL,14,FKuda, who will be joined by a female
OL,15,FRusty-spotted cat later this year to
OL,16,Fbegin a breeding programme in a bid to
OL,17,Fsafeguard the species' future.
OL,26,@nD@AO]oD@AOUoD@QO]
